public class DummyMovingAgent
extends eu.su.mas.dedale.mas.AbstractDedaleAgent
This example class start a Dummy agent that will possess two behaviours :
  1. move randomly and test the API methods RandomWalkBehaviour.
  2. send a meaningless message to two other agents SayHelloBehaviour
